2556  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2557  [return: NotNull]
2558  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId);
2559 
2565  [return: NotNull]
2566  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8([NotNull] string str)
2567  {
2568  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2569  {
2570  return IntPtr.Zero;
2571  }
2572 
2573  IntPtr mem = INTERNAL_SDL_malloc(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0').Length);
2574  Marshal.Copy(Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0'), 0, mem, Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0').Length);
2575  return mem;
2576  }
2577 
2584  public static int ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageBoxData, out int buttonId)
2585  {
2586  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
2587  {
2588  flags = messageBoxData.flags,
2589  window = messageBoxData.window,
2590  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.title),
2591  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.message),
2592  numbuttons = messageBoxData.numbuttons
2593  };
2594 
2595  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageBoxData.numbuttons];
2596  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2597 
2598  try
2599  {
2600  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2601  {
2602  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
2603  {
2604  flags = messageBoxData.buttons[i].flags,
2605  buttonId = messageBoxData.buttons[i].buttonId,
2606  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageBoxData.buttons[i].text)
2607  };
2608  }
2609 
2610  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
2611  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
2612  {
2613  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
2614  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
2615  }
2616 
2617  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
2618 
2619  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
2620  if (messageBoxData.colorScheme != null)
2621  {
2622  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
2623  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageBoxData.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
2624  }
2625 
2626  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonId);
2627 
2628  for (int i = 0; i < messageBoxData.numbuttons; i++)
2629  {
2630  INTERNAL_SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
2631  }
2632 
2633  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.message);
2634  INTERNAL_SDL_free(data.title);
2635 
2636  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2637  {
2638  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
2639  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
2640  }
2641 
2642  return result;
2643  }
2644  finally
2645  {
2646  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
2647  {
2648  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
2649  }
2650  }
2651  }

6503  [return: NotNull]
6504  private static uint SdlDefinePixelFormat(PixelType type, [NotNull] uint order, PackedLayout layout, [NotNull] byte bits, [NotNull] byte bytes) => (uint) ((1 << 28) | ((byte) type << 24) | ((byte) order << 20) | ((byte) layout << 16) | (bits << 8) | bytes);

6511  [return: NotNull]
6512  private static byte SdlPixelFlag([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6513 
6519  [return: NotNull]
6520  private static byte SdlPixelType([NotNull] uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);

6543  [return: NotNull]

6551  [return: NotNull]
6552  public static byte SdlBytesPerPixel([NotNull] uint x)
6553  {
6554  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(x))
6555  {
6556  if (x == PixelFormatYuy2 ||
6557  x == PixelFormatUy ||
6558  x == PixelFormatYv)
6559  {
6560  return 2;
6561  }
6562 
6563  return 1;
6564  }
6565 
6566  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6567  }

6574  [return: NotNull]
6575  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatIndexed([NotNull] uint format)
6576  {
6577  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6578  {
6579  return false;
6580  }
6581 
6582  PixelType pType =
6583  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6584  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex1 ||
6585  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex4 ||
6586  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeIndex8;
6587  }
6588 
6594  [return: NotNull]
6595  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatPacked([NotNull] uint format)
6596  {
6597  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6598  {
6599  return false;
6600  }
6601 
6602  PixelType pType =
6603  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6604  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked8 ||
6605  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked16 ||
6606  pType == PixelType.PixelTypePacked32;
6607  }
6608 
6614  [return: NotNull]
6615  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatArray([NotNull] uint format)
6616  {
6617  if (SdlIsPixelFormatFour(format))
6618  {
6619  return false;
6620  }
6621 
6622  PixelType pType =
6623  (PixelType) SdlPixelType(format);
6624  return pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU8 ||
6625  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU16 ||
6626  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayU32 ||
6627  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF16 ||
6628  pType == PixelType.PixelTypeArrayF32;
6629  }
6630 
6636  [return: NotNull]
6637  public static bool SdlIsPixelFormatAlpha([NotNull] uint format)
6638  {
6639  if (SdlIsPixelFormatPacked(format))
6640  {
6641  PackedOrder pOrder =
6642  (PackedOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6643  return pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderARgb ||
6644  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderRGba ||
6645  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderABgr ||
6646  pOrder == PackedOrder.PackedOrderBGra;
6647  }
6648 
6649  if (SdlIsPixelFormatArray(format))
6650  {
6651  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6652  (SdlArrayOrder) SdlPixelOrder(format);
6653  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6654  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6655  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6656  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6657  }
6658 
6659  return false;
6660  }

6667  [return: NotNull]
6668  private static bool SdlIsPixelFormatFour([NotNull] uint format) => (format == 0) && (SdlPixelFlag(format) != 1);
